@APOLLO STATION
#play 6X6X111X11X1
It has been 4 months since last contact.

Apollo Station had been operational less
than a year before it ran into managerial
problems and ceased commercial operation.
A military team sent to requisition parts
from the abandoned base has not returned.

You are an insurance representative for
the company underwriting the station. You
have been tasked with collecting the logs
from the station's computers. With this
data in hand, negligence can be proven and
coverage denied.

You will save your company a lot of money
today. Be proud.
/i
#play 7X8X5X4X2X1
                How to Play

$Control the company drone by pressing
$the UP, DOWN, LEFT, and RIGHT keys.

$Press T to activate your lamp. Battery is
$limited, so use the yellow charging docks
$located throughout the station to refill.

$Use SPACE to activate your blaster. You
$can refill it at the cyan charging docks.
/i
#play 60006
$LOSING A DRONE

If your drone gets damaged or runs out of
battery, don't panic! Discard it and send
in another one. They're cheap and the
company doesn't care how many you use.
/i
#play --I.FSED#Q.D
             APOLLO STATION
$        by LBC

    end
