$Log Entry 1
$▄ ▄ ▄ ▄ ▄ ▄

Section 5.021         Lt. Cdr. Edna Greene
Day 417 (s)(j)              Apollo Station

Captain cheaped out on cleanup last time
we were Lagrangeside. Again. There's a
nasty funk coming from the stasis pods,
and it's not just Specialist Schwartz. If
there's a brand new species of fungus
eating our hull, they'd better name it
after me. Greene out.
/i
#play +F#G#x+CD
$Log Entry 2
$▄ ▄ ▄ ▄ ▄ ▄

Section 5.022         Lt. Cdr. Edna Greene
Day 426 (s)                 Apollo Station

If you're reading this, you've already
seen what happened. If you're military,
take my advice and tow this thing straight
into ß Leonis. If you're from some private
sector outfit, leave this thing the hell
alone. Trust me.

I'm going to hole up in the cafeteria and
drink nutri shakes until things quiet
down. If I'm still alive, you can find me
there.

Greene out.
/i
#zap touch
#restore Cupboard:edna
#unlock
#end
:touch
#lock
